Before installing anything on your computer, make sure you have node installed.



Backend--------

to run the app:
npm run dev

Dependencies:
npm init -y
npm install express
npm install -g nodemon

// its detecting the change and rerun the file.
nodemon server.js

//to install .env file into the project
npm install dotenv

npm install mongoose



Frontend--------

to run:
npm start

npx create-react-app frontend
npm install react-router-dom